name: u can't lose !!!1!
description:
Sprites and 3D Modeling by Lawrence Watusi  https://lawwatusi.itch.io/

Some music used in this game were provided by https://incompetech.com

Other assets used were given under the Creative Commons 0 License.

"Heya, it's me Mr. Sun, your friend with a terrible voice actor! I am almost 100% sure that the level in this game is impossible to die in, You can't lose at all it's a win win situation why even bother coming by??? If you're gonna download this game that means you are trying to test my obviously correct judgement. Good luck with that haha."

Use the Arrow Keys to move and jump!
